headline: The Latest Innovation from CHIPS AHOY! Is…Not A Cookie?! Introducing New CHIPS AHOY! Baked Bites - Bite-Sized Blondies to Satisfy Your Sweet Tooth
summary: CHIPS AHOY! is introducing its latest innovation – and it's NOT a cookie! New CHIPS AHOY! Baked Bites, Blondie variety, brings the CHIPS AHOY! chocolate chip cookie taste fans love, reimagined in a soft-baked treat, delivering a classic baked favorite in a convenient, snackable form.
